        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="F404A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To put this World down,<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 like a Bundle -</l>
                    <l>And walk steady, away, </l>
                    <l>Requires Energy - possibly Agony - </l>
                    <l>'Tis the Scarlet way </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Trodden with straight renunciation</l>
                    <l>By the Son of God - </l>
                    <l>Later, his faint Confederates </l>
                    <l>Justify the Road - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Flavors of that old Crucifixion - </l>
                    <l>Filaments of Bloom, Pontius Pilate<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 sowed -</l>
                    <l>Strong Clusters, from Barabbas'<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Tomb - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Sacrament, Saints partook before us - </l>
                    <l>Patent, every drop, </l>
                    <l>With the<add type="alternate" extent="Brand">stamp</add>
 Brand of the Gentile Drinker </l>
                    <l>Who<add type="alternate" extent="indorsed">enforced</add>
 indorsed the Cup -</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
